stringStats.value: A fortress forever besieged by Hea Tumeroks, Dryreach can be a dangerous location for an inexperienced adventurer. The Hea Tumeroks use this fortress as a training ground for their warriors, ensuring that the stalemate involving this fortress will never be resolved. Be careful on wandering out the front gates without a key, as they are locked to prevent the Tumerok from gaining entry.
